1.text: Clear out the oven before you clean it.

2.text: Remove large food particles from the bottom of the oven.
2.vid: /1/11/Clean the Bottom of an Oven Step 2.360p.mp4

4.text: Wipe the bottom of your oven with a damp rag or paper towel.
4.vid: /7/7e/Clean the Bottom of an Oven Step 4.360p.mp4

5.text: Put on rubber cleaning gloves and safety glasses.

6.text: Lay down newspapers or paper towels on the floor in front of the oven.
6.vid: /4/48/Clean the Bottom of an Oven Step 6.360p.mp4

7.text: Spray the cleaner onto the bottom of the oven using a sweeping motion.
7.vid: /c/c1/Clean the Bottom of an Oven Step 7.360p.mp4

8.text: Let the cleaner sit for at least 30 minutes.

9.text: Wipe the bottom of the oven clean with a damp cloth.
9.vid: /f/f5/Clean the Bottom of an Oven Step 9.360p.mp4

10.text: Use baking soda and vinegar to clean without toxic chemicals.
10.vid: /3/3b/Clean the Bottom of an Oven Step 10.360p.mp4

11.text: Bake lemons in your oven to clean the bottom.
11.vid: /d/d4/Clean the Bottom of an Oven Step 11.360p.mp4

12.text: Spread salt onto the bottom of the oven to clean it.
